headline: Why the Trump Organization is suing Capital One
summary: President Trump's family business, the Trump Organization, is suing Capital One (COF). It presents a unique problem for the financial institution for a number of reasons, Yahoo Finance Banking Reporter David Hollerith explains why in the video above. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here. This post was written by Stephanie Mikulich.

headline: Trump Organization accuses ‘woke’ Capital One of de-banking
summary: The lender de-banked some 300 Trump Organization accounts because it believed “the political tide at the moment favored doing so,” a lawsuit contends. Eric Trump has suggested more big banks may be targeted.
